    "refcode_long": "Counsels on Sabbath School Work, p. 95.2 (Ellen Gould White)",
    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Sabbath school worker, which will you meet, the standard of Christ or that of the world? Oh, will you say, &ldquo;I will lift the cross and follow Jesus&rdquo;? Will you not cultivate His tenderness in persuasion, His earnestness in exhortation, and exemplify the exalted principles of the truth, manifesting in life and character what the religion of Christ has done for you? Shall we not all heed the exhortation of the apostle, &ldquo;Put ye on the Lord Jesus Christ, and make not provision for the flesh, to fulfill the lusts thereof&rdquo;?",
    "puborder": 266,
    "translations": [
