    "content": "Try it for one year, you who are educators and teachers in our Sabbath and day schools, and see if you will not be able to say, &ldquo;The Lord hath wrought wondrously for us, for many souls have been brought to the Master, as precious sheaves for the heavenly garner.&rdquo;&mdash;<span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"TSS 45.1\" data-link=\"121.171\"><em>Testimonies on Sabbath-School Work</em>, 45, 46</span>.",
